# immich-go Docker

A simple Docker image for running immich-go against an Immich instance.

## Pull

```bash
docker pull ghcr.io/squiter/immich-go-docker:latest
```

## Run

```bash
docker run --rm ghcr.io/squiter/immich-go-docker:latest --version
```

## Example

```bash
docker run --rm \
  --network immich_default \
  -v /path/to/photos:/photos:ro \
  ghcr.io/squiter/immich-go-docker:latest \
  upload from-icloud \
  --server=http://immich-server:2283 \
  --api-key=YOUR_API_KEY \
  /photos
```